videos.description: Allonzo Trier buries a 3-pointer after a nice pass from Deandre Ayton.
videos.headline: Great ball movement leads to Trier corner triple

videos.description: Rawle Alkins knocks down a triple as Arizona takes a lead halfway through the first half over Colorado.
videos.headline: Alkins buries transition 3-pointer for Arizona

videos.description: Deandre Ayton recovers after getting blocked and gets a tough bucket down low.
videos.headline: Ayton shows off strength in post

videos.description: Deandre Ayton shows off his athleticism with a huge block getting well above the rim.
videos.headline: Ayton elevates for sweet block

videos.description: Deandre Ayton takes off his right shoe while sitting on the bench after collecting three fouls including a technical.
videos.headline: Ayton sits without a shoe in 2nd half

videos.description: Super Bowl MVP Nick Foles watches as Rawle Alkins knocks down a 3-pointer for Arizona.
videos.headline: Arizona alum Foles watches on as Alkins buries deep 3
